MANUAL
 

SHORTCUTS

"_l"   - Toggle "show whitespace"
"_n"   - Toggle between line numbering and ruler
"_p"   - Toggle paste mode
"gqip" - Reformat a paragraph with the commandline tool 'par' (needs to be installed)
"_="   - Auto indent whole file
"_$"   - Strip all trailing whitespaces

"Ctrl-e" - Scroll three lines to the top
"Ctrl-y" - Scroll three lines to the bottom
":Stab" - Interactively set tab width
